import React from "react";
import {
  Box,
  Grid,
  FilledInput,
  Select,
  MenuItem,
  Dialog,
  DialogTitle,
  DialogContent,
  DialogAction,
  Menu,
} from "@material-ui/core";

export default (props) => {
  return (
    <Dialog open={true} fullWidth>
      <DialogTitle>Post a Sponsor</DialogTitle>
      <DialogContent>
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FilledInput placeholder="Title" disableUnderline fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <Select
              fullWidth
              disableUnderline
              variant="filled"
              defaultValue="Online"
            >
              <MenuItem value="Online">Online</MenuItem>
              <MenuItem value="Online">Offline</MenuItem>
              <MenuItem value="Online">Hybrid</MenuItem>
            </Select>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FilledInput placeholder="Organization Name" disableUnderline fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FilledInput placeholder="Organization URL" disableUnderline fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <Select
              fullWidth
              disableUnderline
              variant="filled"
              defaultValue="Online"
            >
              <MenuItem value="Online">Large Scale</MenuItem>
              <MenuItem value="Online">Small Scale</MenuItem>
            </Select>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FilledInput placeholder="Apply Link" disableUnderline fullWidth />
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </DialogContent>
    </Dialog>
  );
};
